sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant API
participant Facade
participant PlaceModel
participant DB

User->>API: POST /places (place data)
API->>Facade: create_place(data)
Facade->>PlaceModel: validate & create place
PlaceModel->>DB: INSERT place
DB-->>PlaceModel: success
PlaceModel-->>Facade: place created
Facade-->>API: return place
API-->>User: 201 Created